Node "broke"
notes "'Dismiss' options appropriate to perception appear. PER to notice 'asshole' is currently 6."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Anita bites her lip as she reaches into her pocket. She pulls out some coins and scrabbles through them. After a moment, her bottom lip quivers and her eyes well up a little.] I... I don't have enough..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I... er... never mind. You can have it anyway, for free." linkto "thanks"  notes "Anita likes the player"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh. How about 10, then?" linkto "thanks2"  notes "Anita likes the player"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Shrug.] Them's the breaks. Tough luck." linkto "DismissPER" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception >= 6 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Shrug.] Them's the breaks. Tough luck." linkto "DismissBADPER" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception < 6 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well... there ARE alternate forms of payment." linkto "perv"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "happy"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Anita smiles warmly, leaning slightly into your hand.] You're really sweet to say that, I haven't heard it in years.  Thanks again for the food, hope to see you around again."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're welcome, Anita." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "sorry"
notes "if you do have food and say this, karma -1.  You get a chance to get it back though.  First two options only available if you have food."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[The girl frowns and sighs.] Story of my life."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just kidding. I got some food, but I'd like a little something in return." linkto "pay"  notes "subtracted karma gets restored"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "Aw, I was just messin. Here you go. [Give Anita food.]" linkto "thanks"  notes "Gives it to her free.  subtracted karma restored, plus the karma for giving it free"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I really am sorry, maybe next time." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
