Node "story"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "You could say that. Name's Anita. My mom dumped me here when I was about 15. Thanks a lot for that, Mom. I'm sure she had her reasons, but hell if I know what they were. Not that it matters. Oh, you should have seen me back then. [She sighs]."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "story2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "story2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "That was before I got sick. We're all sick here, I'm sure you noticed. I was voted prettiest in town 3 years running. Now I cant get within 5 feet of anybody that's not sicker than I am. The first few years I was here, I was able to get by alright. People here were very generous, and outsiders always wanted to help a pretty face."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "story3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "story3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "But as the supplies round here tapered off, so did the generosity. And the more of these damn things I sprouted, the fewer visitors wanted anything to do with me. Now its all I can do to scrape by for the next day. I go 3 or 4 days at a time without eating, at least every few weeks. I know it won't get any better, either.  "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "story4"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "story4"
notes "'Dismiss' options appropriate to perception appear. PER to notice 'asshole' is currently 6."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I'm too disfigured now to make it in another town, and I could never afford to try anyway. If only I were still beautiful, things would be so much better."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Place a hand on her cheek.] Anita, you are still beautiful. Don't ever let anyone tell you different." linkto "happy"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wow, it really does suck to be you." linkto "DismissPER" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception >= 6 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wow, it really does suck to be you." linkto "DismissBADPER" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception < 6 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sure things'll pick up. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
